OL,9,GHello, We’re only three weeks away
OL,10,Gfrom being in the field and there’s
OL,11,Gmore things you need to know! EMF runs
OL,12,Gall Sunday (into the night) Do not
OL,13,Gforget that we run for all of Sunday.
OL,14,GTalks finish by 7pm, but we have a
OL,15,Gfull schedule of entertainment until
OL,16,Gmidnight! You are welcome to remain on
OL,17,Gsite until midday on Monday 20th.
OL,18,GMusic &amp; Performances are go We’ve
OL,19,Gannounced the live music and evening
OL,20,Gcomedy performances! The full Null
